data.text:
The Premier League season is now over but the next campaign will be upon us in no time.

Teams are about to return from their summer breaks to prepare for another monstrous top-flight campaign.

Alongside new transfers, clubs will be revealing their fresh kits for the 2023/24 top-flight campaign.

Champions Manchester City, Arsenal, Liverpool and Crystal Palace have all already revealed their home strips.

With a whole host of announcements still to come, fans are waiting patiently to see their team's colours for the new term.

Here, talkSPORT.com gives you a rundown of all the confirmed kits for next season.
